AUDIO: 'to the other side, you can do that, too. &gt;&gt; Next question. Kind of the specs in size, weight. Where are we kind of at roughly on this? &gt;&gt; Yeah. So, we\'re at the lighter side. Uh, the boat itself is 11 ft. It\'s 35 in wide. Uh, the whole weight is 88 lb. The'

