AUDIO: 'here is 10 years worth of work in a 5 lb football. So, this little guy weighs 5 lb and this is capable of up to 5 kow. So, really the limitation is batteries at this point. So, this thing is been'

[07:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'the last decade or so of my life to get to this thing, but it is pretty darn amazing. It is fully serviceable, but it\'s also super simple. I mean, this is designed basically where the motor is'

