VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'wrapped directly around the impeller, so there is only one moving piece. The bearings inside of this are ceramic. It is designed to live in salt water indefinitely. So, um, super proud of this, super happy to finally be able to'

[07:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'show people this and talk about it. So, and just we also wanted to make this thing super easy to service. I mean, not only can you service this, but this is literally four screws and that bolts in. Plug in your wires and you\'re done. It\'s as easy as a trolling car.'

